    "basic_qualifications": "- 3+ years of data engineering experience<br/>- Experience with data modeling, warehousing and building ETL pipelines<br/>- 3+ years of analyzing and interpreting data with Redshift, Oracle, NoSQL etc. experience<br/>- Experience with SQL",
    "business_category": "entertainment",
